  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 170°C (338°F).",
    "Toast the king prawns on a baking sheet for about 2 minutes or until just cooked.",
    "Mix toasted crumbs with coconut oil, finely chopped garlic, and coriander leaves. Add salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Layer raw king prawns over crumb mixture in an oven-proof dish. Bake for 5-7 minutes or until the top is golden brown.",
    "Serve hot as a snack."
